Aston Villa may be able to sign Cordoba striker Florin Andone for as little as £ 2.5 million .
The Spanish side are poised to be relegated and need to raise funds .
Villa have held talks over 22-year-old Andone earlier this week and will look to strike a bargain for the player .
The player is valued at around £ 6million but Cordoba lose their La Liga status .